0.03  2025-10-29
      - Removed redundant package YaraFFI::Record::YR_RULE.

0.02  2025-10-28
      - Extracted YaraFFI::Event package.
      - Updated SYNOPSIS example.

0.01  2025-10-28
      - module created.
